 a given year\n  // Returns array of InvoiceSummary with month, year, count, and total_revenue\n}\n```\n\n**Key Implementation Details:**\n- Fetches all invoices for the given year\n- Groups by month using `Date.getMonth() + 1` (1-indexed)\n- Returns sorted array by month (1-12)\n- Each summary includes: month, year, invoice count, total revenue\n\n#### getCustomerReport:\n```typescript\nexport function getCustomerReport(\n  db: Database.Database,\n  customerId: string,\n): CustomerReport\n```\n\nReturns: customer_id, invoice_count, total_spent, average_invoice\n\n#### getRevenueByPeriod:\n```typescript\nexport function getRevenueByPeriod(\n  db: Database.Database,\n  start: string,\n  end: string,\n): { total: number; count: number }\n```\n\nReturns total revenue and invoice count for a date range.\n\n## Supporting Functions\n\n### Billing Functions (in `/workspace/src/services/billing.ts`):\n- `calculateSubtotal(lineItems)` - sums quantity × unit_price\n- `applyDiscount(subtotal, discountRate)` - applies discount to subtotal\n- `generateInvoice(db, input)` - creates invoice with calculated totals\n\n### Query Functions (in `/workspace/src/db/queries.ts`):\n- `getInvoiceById(db, id)` - retrieves invoice with line items\n- `createInvoice(db, data)` - inserts invoice and line items\n- `getInvoicesByCustomer(db, customerId)` - retrieves all customer invoices\n\n### Utility Functions:\n- **dates.ts**: formatDate, parseDate, getMonthRange, isDateInRange\n- **format.ts**: formatCurrency, formatPercentage, calculateTax (legacy with bug)\n\n## Database Schema\n\n**invoices table:**\n- id (INTEGER PRIMARY KEY)\n- customer_id (TEXT)\n- date (TEXT, ISO format)\n- subtotal, discount_rate, tax_rate, total (REAL)\n- status (TEXT: draft|sent|paid|cancelled)\n\n**line_items table:**\n- id, invoice_id, description, quantity, unit_price\n\n## Known Issues\n\n1. **calculateInvoiceTotal bug**: Tax is applied to subtotal instead of discounted subtotal\n2. **getInvoicesByDateRange bug**